com.gridgraph.structure.metadata.index

Class GraphDegreeIndex

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.structure.metadata.index.GraphDegreeIndex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GraphDegreeIndex
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Degree index (containing in-, out-, total-degree) definition for a schema
    Note that a GraphDegreeIndex is an instance representing all the 3 degree indices: in-, out- and total-degree. In case a non-null schema is specified, the 3 types of degree indices of the schema will exist. In case a null schema is specified, all the 3 types of total degree indices of all schemas will exist
    Author:
    guobao.chen
